				<li class="cd-faq-title"><h2>Basics</h2></li>
				<li>
					<li style="color:MediumSeaGreen;"> <font size = "+2">Is account registration required?</font></li>
					<div class="cd-faq-content">
						<br>
						Account registration at TeenServ is required for all employers and teenagers.
						This ensures a valid communication channel for all parties involved in any transactions.
						<br>
					</div>
				</li>

				<br>
				<li>
					<li style="color:MediumSeaGreen;"> <font size = "+2">How to create an account?</font></li>
					<div class="cd-faq-content">
						<br>
						Go to the Register page and fill our the register form.
						After creating your account, you can login and start to post/apply jobs. You can also edit or add your personal information in "Profile" Page.
